Mon May 25 02:35:55 UTC 2026 - Jonatas Gonçalves <jonatas.sgoncalves@gmail.com>

- Update to version 0.1.2
  * Reworked tray icon backend replacing pystray/Pillow with
    GTK3 + AyatanaAppIndicator implementation
  * Added Cairo-based high quality tray icon rendering with
    dynamic controller labels (P1/P2/etc)
  * Added Flatpak-aware icon path detection and autostart setup
  * Added evdev force-feedback support for controller vibration
  * Added low battery vibration alerts with configurable pulse patterns
    for 50%, 25% and 15% battery levels
  * Added automatic controller event device discovery using MAC matching
  * Added persistent rumble device handles for improved FF stability
  * Added cleanup of rumble handles on controller disconnect
  * Improved controller timeout cleanup and resource handling
  * Added native GTK main loop integration
  * Improved dynamic controller mapping logic
  * Added support for local development icon directory detection
  * Reworked tray icon scaling and rendering quality
  * Improved logging messages and controller detection diagnostics
  * Removed legacy pystray and Pillow dependencies 

